15
00:02:12,710 --> 00:02:13,110
Yes.

16
00:02:15,510 --> 00:02:16,300
Guo Zhuang.

17
00:02:18,670 --> 00:02:20,130
I'm not familiar with him,

18
00:02:22,070 --> 00:02:24,200
but since he was once an Imperial Guard

19
00:02:24,829 --> 00:02:26,030
and followed Lu Tong,

20
00:02:28,070 --> 00:02:29,030
he's a meritorious minister

21
00:02:29,030 --> 00:02:31,430
who helped me eliminate Queen Wei's party.

22
00:02:34,470 --> 00:02:36,350
To think it'd end up like this.

23
00:02:37,030 --> 00:02:38,230
Guo Zhuang was killed

24
00:02:38,710 --> 00:02:39,680
because I fell

25
00:02:39,710 --> 00:02:41,030
