26
00:02:43,829 --> 00:02:45,360
Please punish me, Your Highness.

27
00:02:45,360 --> 00:02:46,630
Get up.

28
00:02:47,140 --> 00:02:48,630
You're seriously injured.

29
00:02:48,630 --> 00:02:49,780
You must've done your best.

30
00:02:49,780 --> 00:02:50,840
That's not a crime.

31
00:02:52,230 --> 00:02:52,960
Lu Lingfeng.

32
00:02:53,590 --> 00:02:55,070
Do you know that these days,

33
00:02:55,070 --> 00:02:57,060
His Highness couldn't sleep or eat

34
00:02:57,470 --> 00:02:58,540
because of you?

35
00:02:59,190 --> 00:03:00,320
Don't tell him that.

36
00:03:01,150 --> 00:03:03,350
I didn't eat because I have no appetite.

37
00:03:06,350 --> 00:03:07,550
This Ghost Market...

38
00:03:08,870 --> 00:03:10,150
I'm willing to lead the elites

39
00:03:10,150 --> 00:03:11,110
to subdue Ghost Market.

40
00:03:11,110 --> 00:03:12,170
Then there won't be

41
00:03:12,290 --> 00:03:13,930
a place outside the law in Chang'an.

42
00:03:13,930 --> 00:03:15,270
The Mara doesn't just kill

43
00:03:15,270 --> 00:03:17,070
and take livers in Ghost Market.

44
00:03:17,910 --> 00:03:18,570
I heard that

45
00:03:19,110 --> 00:03:20,610
there are many who rely on Ghost Market

46
00:03:20,610 --> 00:03:21,540
to make a living.

47
00:03:21,930 --> 00:03:23,390
Though many are refugees,

48
00:03:23,630 --> 00:03:25,700
they are still the people of Tang after all.

49
00:03:25,700 --> 00:03:26,870
The court should find a way

50
00:03:26,870 --> 00:03:28,100
to manage it

51
00:03:28,310 --> 00:03:29,370
and take care of it.

52
00:03:29,590 --> 00:03:31,310
Your Highness is broad-minded,

53
00:03:31,310 --> 00:03:33,310
serving the country and the people.

54
00:03:34,190 --> 00:03:35,450
What are you doing now?

55
00:03:35,650 --> 00:03:37,150
Your Highness, please give the order

56
00:03:37,150 --> 00:03:39,329
to get rid of the Mara's Defeat mural in Chengfo Temple.

57
00:03:39,329 --> 00:03:39,829
This...

58
00:03:44,460 --> 00:03:45,270
A few days ago,

59
00:03:45,950 --> 00:03:46,910
Kong Mao's father

60
00:03:46,910 --> 00:03:48,640
took people to Chengfo Temple.

61
00:03:48,870 --> 00:03:49,910
They failed to remove the mural

62
00:03:49,910 --> 00:03:51,170
and even got scolded by

63
00:03:51,190 --> 00:03:52,430
people from the Princess' Palace

64
00:03:52,430 --> 00:03:53,829
and had his salary confiscated.

65
00:03:53,829 --> 00:03:55,440
Administrator Du Ming of Yongzhou

66
00:03:55,440 --> 00:03:57,350
was ordered to send troops to Chengfo Temple

67
00:03:57,350 --> 00:03:59,350
to protect the mural.

68
00:03:59,680 --> 00:04:00,910
I received an invitation

69
00:04:00,910 --> 00:04:02,430
from my aunt to unveil

70
00:04:02,450 --> 00:04:03,230
the greatest

71
00:04:03,260 --> 00:04:04,800
mural of Tang with her

72
00:04:04,830 --> 00:04:06,310
on Mingyin Festival.

73
00:04:06,870 --> 00:04:09,110
Tell me. How can we remove the mural?

74
00:04:09,670 --> 00:04:10,730
It must be removed.

75
00:04:13,630 --> 00:04:14,510
Did you...

76
00:04:18,070 --> 00:04:19,110
really meet Mara

77
00:04:19,510 --> 00:04:21,769
who came out of the mural in Ghost Market?

78
00:04:24,740 --> 00:04:25,480
Regardless whether

79
00:04:25,480 --> 00:04:27,010
Mara broke out of the mural,

80
00:04:27,070 --> 00:04:28,290
they must be related.

81
00:04:28,670 --> 00:04:29,630
Remove the mural

82
00:04:29,970 --> 00:04:31,230
for peace in Chang'an.

83
00:04:41,990 --> 00:04:43,250
You're badly injured.

84
00:04:43,590 --> 00:04:44,350
Let me send you back

85
00:04:44,350 --> 00:04:45,110
to rest.

86
00:04:45,470 --> 00:04:47,260
Your Highness, please give the order to remove the mural.

87
00:04:47,260 --> 00:04:47,990
Lu Lingfeng!

88
00:04:51,350 --> 00:04:52,210
You're putting

89
00:04:52,670 --> 00:04:54,530
His Highness in a difficult spot.

90
00:05:05,180 --> 00:05:07,130
[Supreme Court]

91
00:05:27,150 --> 00:05:27,730
Guards!

92
00:05:30,950 --> 00:05:31,710
Let me ask you.

93
00:05:31,710 --> 00:05:32,480
Who was here?

94
00:05:32,670 --> 00:05:34,909
Who took away my investigation journal?

95
00:05:34,909 --> 00:05:35,830
Mr. Su.

96
00:05:36,030 --> 00:05:37,070
What Mr. Su?

97
00:05:37,990 --> 00:05:39,500
I'm Su Wuming.

98
00:06:20,510 --> 00:06:21,190
Senior.

99
00:06:27,750 --> 00:06:28,350
Junior.

100
00:06:29,150 --> 00:06:30,030
People say

101
00:06:30,750 --> 00:06:33,680
if you survive a great disaster, you will be blessed.

102
00:06:34,030 --> 00:06:36,960
You must pull yourself together as soon as possible.

103
00:06:38,350 --> 00:06:38,909
Senior.

104
00:06:40,230 --> 00:06:41,960
Why are you back in the capital?

105
00:06:43,230 --> 00:06:44,670
I'm the new

106
00:06:44,900 --> 00:06:47,100
Deputy President of the Supreme Court.

107
00:06:48,860 --> 00:06:50,659
Acting Deputy President.

108
00:06:52,110 --> 00:06:52,909
Su Wuming!

109
00:06:53,350 --> 00:06:54,320
Su Wuming!

110
00:06:55,690 --> 00:06:56,600
You young one.

111
00:06:57,110 --> 00:06:58,570
You run faster than me.

112
00:07:00,880 --> 00:07:02,410
Lu Lingfeng.

113
00:07:03,310 --> 00:07:05,270
I just put lesser incense

114
00:07:05,350 --> 00:07:06,670
and you woke up!

115
00:07:07,470 --> 00:07:08,330
Let me tell you.

116
00:07:08,390 --> 00:07:10,190
My treatment for you this time

117
00:07:10,230 --> 00:07:11,280
is very special.

118
00:07:11,870 --> 00:07:12,610
It's mainly

119
00:07:12,630 --> 00:07:14,090
to restore your vitality.

120
00:07:14,550 --> 00:07:16,030
You're a martial artist.

121
00:07:16,510 --> 00:07:17,750
If you don't

122
00:07:17,750 --> 00:07:19,150
fully recover this time,

123
00:07:19,510 --> 00:07:21,270
you can't even beat others in fighting.

124
00:07:21,270 --> 00:07:22,070
Fei!

125
00:07:23,670 --> 00:07:24,730
Why did you lie to me

126
00:07:25,630 --> 00:07:26,950
about Guo Zhuang?

127
00:07:27,070 --> 00:07:27,530
Well...

128
00:07:29,550 --> 00:07:30,030
Let go.

129
00:07:30,430 --> 00:07:31,110
Let go!

130
00:07:31,350 --> 00:07:32,310
Let go!

131
00:07:33,590 --> 00:07:35,190
Fei saved your life.

132
00:07:35,390 --> 00:07:36,830
Why are you blaming him?

133
00:07:36,990 --> 00:07:37,550
Exactly.

134
00:07:43,270 --> 00:07:44,750
Give me the investigation journal.

135
00:07:44,750 --> 00:07:46,310
I need to solve this case as soon as possible.

136
00:07:46,310 --> 00:07:47,100
Enough.

137
00:07:47,670 --> 00:07:49,070
Focus on recuperating now

138
00:07:49,070 --> 00:07:49,950
instead of

139
00:07:50,360 --> 00:07:51,480
investigating.

140
00:07:53,180 --> 00:07:54,110
Give me ten days.

141
00:07:55,070 --> 00:07:55,880
Well...

142
00:07:56,260 --> 00:07:57,520
Eight days will do too.

143
00:07:57,720 --> 00:07:59,920
As long as you listen to me,

144
00:08:00,360 --> 00:08:02,510
I guarantee your health will be as good as before.

145
00:08:02,510 --> 00:08:03,190
Shut up!

146
00:08:05,770 --> 00:08:06,410
Get out.

147
00:08:06,820 --> 00:08:08,350
I won't...

148
00:08:13,670 --> 00:08:15,510
Fei's right.

149
00:08:15,550 --> 00:08:16,470
Right now,

150
00:08:16,630 --> 00:08:18,390
your recuperation is key.

151
00:08:18,750 --> 00:08:20,040
Because of this case,

152
00:08:20,040 --> 00:08:21,710
I was transferred back to the capital.

153
00:08:21,710 --> 00:08:23,190
To be promoted to

154
00:08:23,190 --> 00:08:24,590
Deputy President,

155
00:08:25,190 --> 00:08:27,380
I must earn merits

156
00:08:27,470 --> 00:08:28,910
with this case.

157
00:08:29,810 --> 00:08:30,630
How about

158
00:08:30,870 --> 00:08:32,710
you give this case to me?

159
00:08:33,909 --> 00:08:37,320
Mr. Lu, please help me.

160
00:08:44,690 --> 00:08:46,690
Give me the investigation journal.

161
00:08:46,950 --> 00:08:48,350
Hurry up and send it to me.

162
00:08:50,550 --> 00:08:51,630
You two became major officials

163
00:08:51,630 --> 00:08:52,790
all of a sudden.

164
00:08:52,870 --> 00:08:53,710
Why are you

165
00:08:53,710 --> 00:08:54,900
even rivals?

166
00:08:56,330 --> 00:08:57,590
We haven't seen each other for months.

167
00:08:57,590 --> 00:08:59,230
You didn't even prepare a jar of wine

168
00:08:59,230 --> 00:09:00,560
and two chickens for me.

169
00:09:08,510 --> 00:09:09,110
Princess.

170
00:09:09,990 --> 00:09:11,070
Where are you going?

171
00:09:11,070 --> 00:09:12,710
Lu Lingfeng had been missing for days.

172
00:09:12,710 --> 00:09:14,170
I heard it was a close call.

173
00:09:14,550 --> 00:09:15,510
I'll go check on him.

174
00:09:15,510 --> 00:09:16,140
No way.

175
00:09:16,670 --> 00:09:18,270
Lu Lingfeng went straight to Eastern Palace last night.

176
00:09:18,270 --> 00:09:20,190
I heard the Crown Prince welcomed him in the rain.

177
00:09:20,190 --> 00:09:22,070
He is the trusted subordinate of Eastern Palace.

178
00:09:22,070 --> 00:09:22,850
So what?

179
00:09:23,510 --> 00:09:24,830
Lu Lingfeng's disappearance

180
00:09:24,830 --> 00:09:26,550
might've been Eastern Palace's plan.

181
00:09:26,550 --> 00:09:27,910
Now that you and Crown Prince are at odds,

182
00:09:27,910 --> 00:09:29,840
there will be a war sooner or later.

183
00:09:29,910 --> 00:09:31,310
I've received the report.

184
00:09:31,310 --> 00:09:32,190
They are planning

185
00:09:32,190 --> 00:09:33,220
to attack you.

186
00:09:33,630 --> 00:09:35,230
Aren't you allowing them to do so

187
00:09:35,230 --> 00:09:36,870
by going to the Supreme Court now?

188
00:09:36,870 --> 00:09:37,550
Enough.

189
00:09:38,270 --> 00:09:39,870
I don't want to listen to you.

190
00:09:39,990 --> 00:09:40,450
Then...

191
00:09:41,240 --> 00:09:43,770
you need to be protected by guards and horses.

192
00:09:43,910 --> 00:09:44,740
No need.

193
00:09:45,230 --> 00:09:45,910
Princess!

194
00:09:46,390 --> 00:09:47,920
Didn't you transfer me here

195
00:09:48,030 --> 00:09:49,330
to plot something big?

196
00:09:50,230 --> 00:09:51,390
Always be careful.

197
00:09:51,870 --> 00:09:53,030
You taught me that.

198
00:09:54,110 --> 00:09:54,720
Fine.

199
00:09:55,390 --> 00:09:56,610
I'll have some tea.

200
00:09:57,390 --> 00:09:58,850
Help me prepare quickly.

201
00:10:02,310 --> 00:10:02,910
Princess.

202
00:10:03,460 --> 00:10:04,790
I'll say one more thing.

203
00:10:05,550 --> 00:10:06,390
Lu Lingfeng

204
00:10:06,790 --> 00:10:08,320
didn't solve the case well.

205
00:10:08,750 --> 00:10:10,350
Why don't you take this chance

206
00:10:10,350 --> 00:10:12,600
to cut off the wings of the Eastern Palace

207
00:10:12,600 --> 00:10:14,860
and kill him to prevent future troubles?

208
00:10:18,230 --> 00:10:19,590
It hurts so much.

209
00:10:19,950 --> 00:10:20,390
You...

210
00:10:21,030 --> 00:10:21,910
Slap yourself

211
00:10:22,510 --> 00:10:24,020
until I come back.

212
00:10:33,700 --> 00:10:41,330
[Supreme Court]

213
00:10:45,430 --> 00:10:47,400
Greetings, Your Highness.

214
00:10:51,590 --> 00:10:52,790
Where is Lu Lingfeng?

215
00:10:55,680 --> 00:10:57,150
I-I don't know.

216
00:10:57,430 --> 00:10:58,110
Su Wuming.

217
00:10:58,630 --> 00:10:59,870
He's badly injured.

218
00:10:59,990 --> 00:11:01,630
Shouldn't you be by his side?

219
00:11:02,190 --> 00:11:02,550
I...

220
00:11:04,620 --> 00:11:05,820
Your Highness.

221
00:11:06,250 --> 00:11:07,680
Mr. Lu is seriously injured,

222
00:11:07,680 --> 00:11:08,880
but he should be fine.

223
00:11:09,150 --> 00:11:09,990
An hour ago,

224
00:11:10,230 --> 00:11:12,430
I saw him with his armor and spear

225
00:11:12,470 --> 00:11:13,330
riding a horse.

226
00:11:13,440 --> 00:11:14,430
I really admire

227
00:11:14,830 --> 00:11:16,500
his majestic aura.

228
00:11:21,740 --> 00:11:24,660
Where can he go when he's seriously injured?

229
00:11:27,910 --> 00:11:28,510
Princess.

230
00:11:29,100 --> 00:11:30,140
I think I know

231
00:11:31,090 --> 00:11:32,270
where he went.

232
00:11:32,650 --> 00:11:35,190
[Chengfo Temple]

233
00:11:35,310 --> 00:11:37,510
You can't enter the temple with a spear.

234
00:11:38,430 --> 00:11:39,110
Step aside.

235
00:11:39,380 --> 00:11:40,630
Soldiers of Yongzhou Government

236
00:11:40,630 --> 00:11:42,020
are ordered to guard Chengfo Temple.

237
00:11:42,020 --> 00:11:44,220
No one is allowed to enter with weapons.

238
00:11:44,240 --> 00:11:45,300
Please step back.

239
00:11:45,950 --> 00:11:47,280
Get out of the way!

240
00:12:02,750 --> 00:12:04,600
I, Lu Lingfeng, will remove the mural

241
00:12:04,600 --> 00:12:05,860
to suppress the demon.

242
00:12:06,230 --> 00:12:07,590
If it's a crime,

243
00:12:07,610 --> 00:12:09,340
I'll take the responsibility.

244
00:12:09,350 --> 00:12:10,950
It has nothing to do with you.

245
00:12:12,150 --> 00:12:12,750
Move back!

246
00:12:14,590 --> 00:12:15,320
Try to stop me

247
00:12:16,110 --> 00:12:18,150
and meet my spear.

248
00:12:51,710 --> 00:12:52,650
Qin Xiaobai?

249
00:12:52,950 --> 00:12:53,530
Move!

250
00:12:55,430 --> 00:12:56,750
Lu Lingfeng.

251
00:12:57,700 --> 00:12:58,750
Why do you want to

252
00:12:58,770 --> 00:13:00,560
destroy my Mara's Defeat?

253
00:13:01,670 --> 00:13:03,030
If you weren't arrogant

254
00:13:03,660 --> 00:13:05,790
and claimed Mara would break out of the mural,

255
00:13:05,790 --> 00:13:06,630
Chang'an's people

256
00:13:06,630 --> 00:13:08,020
wouldn't be in panic.

257
00:13:08,750 --> 00:13:09,780
If you don't move,

258
00:13:10,790 --> 00:13:11,600
I'll kill you

259
00:13:11,630 --> 00:13:13,360
with my spear.

260
00:13:16,590 --> 00:13:18,110
I, Qin Xiaobai,

261
00:13:19,150 --> 00:13:21,080
haven't made the finishing touch.

262
00:13:22,020 --> 00:13:23,940
It's agonizing.

263
00:13:24,470 --> 00:13:26,030
I just want to die.

264
00:13:26,910 --> 00:13:28,150
Come on.

265
00:13:29,360 --> 00:13:31,360
You're from the Lu family of Fanyang

266
00:13:31,550 --> 00:13:34,150
and the former general of the Imperial Guards.

267
00:13:34,190 --> 00:13:35,830
For Chang'an black tea and Sky-scraping Tower,

268
00:13:35,830 --> 00:13:37,320
you were involved.

269
00:13:37,910 --> 00:13:39,740
You can be considered a big shot.

270
00:13:40,490 --> 00:13:42,050
I can make do with you being

271
00:13:42,390 --> 00:13:43,430
my executioner.

272
00:13:43,920 --> 00:13:44,440
Come on.

273
00:13:46,310 --> 00:13:47,670
It’s my destiny

274
00:13:47,780 --> 00:13:49,950
to die in front of the mural.

275
00:13:50,110 --> 00:13:50,750
Fine.

276
00:13:52,030 --> 00:13:52,790
In that case,

277
00:13:53,390 --> 00:13:54,590
I'll grant your wish.

278
00:13:56,220 --> 00:13:56,910
Stop!

279
00:14:00,190 --> 00:14:00,920
Lu Lingfeng.

280
00:14:01,230 --> 00:14:02,260
Don't you know

281
00:14:02,260 --> 00:14:03,720
murder is a capital crime?

282
00:14:05,110 --> 00:14:06,570
If I can destroy the mural,

283
00:14:06,620 --> 00:14:07,770
what's with a death?

284
00:14:09,150 --> 00:14:09,880
Lu Lingfeng.

285
00:14:14,030 --> 00:14:14,710
Great.

286
00:14:15,500 --> 00:14:16,670
You're back.

287
00:14:17,390 --> 00:14:18,550
Are you hurt badly?

288
00:14:23,670 --> 00:14:24,830
What are you doing?

289
00:14:25,070 --> 00:14:26,870
Qin Xiaobai was hired by me.

290
00:14:27,310 --> 00:14:28,770
Why do you want to kill him?

291
00:14:28,870 --> 00:14:30,070
There is law in Tang.

292
00:14:30,390 --> 00:14:31,810
If you stab him,

293
00:14:31,870 --> 00:14:33,660
even I can't save you.

294
00:14:37,200 --> 00:14:38,230
