00:27:25,470 --> 00:27:28,070
The moonlight is bright tonight.

586
00:27:28,950 --> 00:27:30,950
Why don't you do the finishing touch

587
00:27:32,150 --> 00:27:33,410
under this moonlight?

588
00:27:33,720 --> 00:27:34,580
Three days ago,

589
00:27:34,830 --> 00:27:35,670
when Her Highness came to Chengfo Temple,

590
00:27:35,670 --> 00:27:36,870
she made a threat that

591
00:27:36,910 --> 00:27:38,190
if you couldn't get the job done

592
00:27:38,190 --> 00:27:39,850
before Mingyin Festival, she...

593
00:27:39,850 --> 00:27:41,710
She'd kill me?

594
00:27:42,350 --> 00:27:44,400
She didn't say it that way.

595
00:27:44,870 --> 00:27:46,080
I, Qin Xiaobai,

596
00:27:46,110 --> 00:27:47,790
have drawn all the murals,

597
00:27:48,340 --> 00:27:49,710
loved all the women,

598
00:27:49,750 --> 00:27:50,710
and had all the wine

599
00:27:50,710 --> 00:27:51,790
that I wanted.

600
00:27:51,910 --> 00:27:53,230
I have no regrets.

601
00:27:53,830 --> 00:27:54,760
Anyone can

602
00:27:55,030 --> 00:27:56,790
take my life anytime.

603
00:27:57,990 --> 00:27:59,150
But... But the criticism of you

604
00:27:59,150 --> 00:28:00,350
from the art world of Chang'an

605
00:28:00,350 --> 00:28:02,590
will be passed down to future generations.

606
00:28:02,590 --> 00:28:04,230
How many decent painters are there in Chang'an?

607
00:28:04,230 --> 00:28:05,870
How are they qualified to talk about me?

608
00:28:05,870 --> 00:28:07,090
To... Tonight,

609
00:28:07,590 --> 00:28:09,480
Dan Zhu who paints murals at Guangde Temple

610
00:28:09,480 --> 00:28:10,950
invited a few fellows

611
00:28:11,530 --> 00:28:13,590
to have a drink at Dong's Restaurant.

612
00:28:13,710 --> 00:28:15,070
They said at dinner that

613
00:28:15,550 --> 00:28:16,790
you've not only lost your touch, Senior,

614
00:28:16,790 --> 00:28:17,190
but...

615
00:28:18,630 --> 00:28:20,430
But also exhausted your talent.

616
00:28:20,830 --> 00:28:22,510
Senior, you can hit me if you want.

617
00:28:22,510 --> 00:28:23,910
It wasn't me who said that.

618
00:28:23,910 --> 00:28:24,950
I just heard it.

619
00:28:25,390 --> 00:28:26,720
If I knew how to use a knife,

620
00:28:26,720 --> 00:28:27,670
I would have rushed in

621
00:28:27,670 --> 00:28:28,330
and killed those jerks

622
00:28:28,330 --> 00:28:30,190
who were slandering you, Senior.

623
00:28:37,150 --> 00:28:38,550
Let them

624
00:28:39,960 --> 00:28:41,550
say whatever they want.

625
00:28:45,830 --> 00:28:46,430
Senior.

626
00:28:47,630 --> 00:28:49,820
You've been delaying the finishing touch.

627
00:28:49,820 --> 00:28:51,480
You must have no inspiration.

628
00:28:56,750 --> 00:28:58,080
I actually have an idea.

629
00:29:07,110 --> 00:29:09,110
What, Senior?

630
00:29:09,910 --> 00:29:11,840
You've also heard of Flying Light?

631
00:29:12,470 --> 00:29:15,000
This thing appeared in Dongdu a few years ago.

632
00:29:15,230 --> 00:29:15,790
I heard

633
00:29:16,230 --> 00:29:17,670
the murals that use this as the finishing touch

634
00:29:17,670 --> 00:29:19,230
are the most attractive to pilgrims.

635
00:29:19,230 --> 00:29:21,350
Its eyes shine extraordinarily brightly,

636
00:29:21,350 --> 00:29:22,080
and they even

637
00:29:22,310 --> 00:29:23,720
move as

638
00:29:24,030 --> 00:29:25,030
the viewers move.

639
00:29:25,310 --> 00:29:25,790
Now,

640
00:29:27,630 --> 00:29:28,830
just over a month ago,

641
00:29:29,510 --> 00:29:31,670
the best Flying Light appeared in Chang'an.

642
00:29:31,670 --> 00:29:33,270
Many people only have average painting skills,

643
00:29:33,270 --> 00:29:34,400
but with this Flying Light,

644
00:29:34,400 --> 00:29:35,380
they received lots of offers of mural painting

645
00:29:35,380 --> 00:29:36,710
and made loads of money.

646
00:29:37,350 --> 00:29:39,210
Although I haven't bought it yet,

647
00:29:39,320 --> 00:29:39,880
I believe

648
00:29:39,920 --> 00:29:41,680
nothing is impossible for a willing heart.

649
00:29:41,680 --> 00:29:42,680
I will definitely

650
00:29:42,690 --> 00:29:44,750
buy the Flying Light for you, Senior.

651
00:29:46,270 --> 00:29:47,510
A few years ago,

652
00:29:49,030 --> 00:29:49,830
in Dongdu?

653
00:29:51,070 --> 00:29:52,590
You are so ignorant.

654
00:29:53,600 --> 00:29:55,240
That demon has been around

655
00:29:55,270 --> 00:29:56,710
for hundreds of years.

656
00:29:57,150 --> 00:29:58,030
Hundreds of years?

657
00:29:58,030 --> 00:29:58,510
Zu.

658
00:29:59,750 --> 00:30:01,070
You lowly slave.

659
00:30:01,270 --> 00:30:02,150
The reason why I redeemed you

660
00:30:02,150 --> 00:30:03,470
is that I wanted you to stay by my side

661
00:30:03,470 --> 00:30:04,590
and learn the Way of Danqing.

662
00:30:04,590 --> 00:30:05,590
Not only do you rest on your laurels,

663
00:30:05,590 --> 00:30:06,670
you also came up with such an idea.

664
00:30:06,670 --> 00:30:08,590
Would I, Qin Xiaobai, go this low?

665
00:30:09,220 --> 00:30:10,310
Get out!

666
00:30:20,380 --> 00:30:21,910
Qin Xiaobai spent every day

667
00:30:22,100 --> 00:30:24,510
thinking about the finishing touch for the mural.

668
00:30:24,510 --> 00:30:25,810
I peeped from outside the window

669
00:30:25,810 --> 00:30:27,190
and saw him crying a lot.

670
00:30:27,830 --> 00:30:28,590
To be honest,

671
00:30:28,990 --> 00:30:30,650
even I wish he could start soon

672
00:30:30,870 --> 00:30:32,470
and stop torturing himself.

673
00:30:32,950 --> 00:30:34,470
In that case,

674
00:30:34,690 --> 00:30:36,650
there's nothing suspicious.

675
00:30:38,430 --> 00:30:38,890
Indeed.

676
00:30:39,710 --> 00:30:40,230
But

677
00:30:40,510 --> 00:30:42,060
his junior, Zu,

678
00:30:42,260 --> 00:30:43,710
has been wandering around.

679
00:30:43,710 --> 00:30:44,870
He has been to

680
00:30:44,910 --> 00:30:46,020
almost every painting shop in both West Market and East Market.

681
00:30:46,020 --> 00:30:47,210
So a painter went to some painting shops.

682
00:30:47,210 --> 00:30:48,340
What's the big deal?

683
00:30:48,470 --> 00:30:50,510
If he was just buying some ordinary paints,

684
00:30:50,510 --> 00:30:52,150
it wouldn't have been a big deal.

685
00:30:52,150 --> 00:30:52,990
But he went to

686
00:30:53,010 --> 00:30:54,190
Shenzhu Painting Shop in East Market alone

687
00:30:54,190 --> 00:30:55,310
three times a day,

688
00:30:55,750 --> 00:30:57,350
and got kicked out in the end.

689
00:30:58,320 --> 00:30:59,950
[Shenzhu Painting Shop]

690
00:30:59,210 --> 00:31:00,140
It seems that he broke

691
00:31:00,140 --> 00:31:00,950
their rules.

692
00:31:01,230 --> 00:31:02,190
He wanted to buy

693
00:31:02,470 --> 00:31:03,470
some valuable paint

694
00:31:03,470 --> 00:31:05,550
without making a reservation in advance.

695
00:31:05,550 --> 00:31:06,880
Shenzhu Painting Shop?

696
00:31:07,670 --> 00:31:08,800
What a coincidence.

697
00:31:08,830 --> 00:31:10,890
Bi Chengye also went there every day.

698
00:31:12,350 --> 00:31:14,270
The owner of Cloud Tower

699
00:31:14,290 --> 00:31:16,220
visited a painting shop every day?

700
00:31:16,410 --> 00:31:17,210
That's right.

701
00:31:18,100 --> 00:31:18,960
I asked around.

702
00:31:19,160 --> 00:31:20,630
Shenzhu Painting Shop's owner

703
00:31:20,630 --> 00:31:21,430
is Bi Chengye.

704
00:31:21,850 --> 00:31:22,830
The so-called shopkeeper

705
00:31:22,830 --> 00:31:24,560
is actually just a accountant.

706
00:31:26,490 --> 00:31:27,870
That's quite

707
00:31:28,690 --> 00:31:29,780
interesting.

708
00:31:30,010 --> 00:31:32,120
[Peaceful Wind]

709
00:31:36,550 --> 00:31:38,310
Fed is taking care of Lu Lingfeng.

710
00:31:38,310 --> 00:31:39,340
He should be fine.

711
00:31:39,630 --> 00:31:42,480
I'll show you around the painting shops.

712
00:31:42,740 --> 00:31:43,470
Cheer up.

713
00:31:53,230 --> 00:31:53,690
Please.

714
00:32:03,490 --> 00:32:05,750
[Shenzhu Painting Shop]

715
00:32:21,740 --> 00:32:22,470
Sir.

716
00:32:23,120 --> 00:32:24,120
I'm really sorry.

717
00:32:24,820 --> 00:32:25,550
It's okay.

718
00:32:26,070 --> 00:32:26,800
Are you okay?

719
00:32:27,100 --> 00:32:27,920
I'm fine.

720
00:32:28,030 --> 00:32:30,100
I don't know why my legs got weak.

721
00:32:30,830 --> 00:32:32,430
Thank you for your help, Sir.

722
00:32:43,740 --> 00:32:44,270
Thief!

723
00:32:51,650 --> 00:32:52,850
You beautiful thief!

724
00:32:53,000 --> 00:32:54,070
Give my treasure back!

725
00:32:54,070 --> 00:32:55,470
Beautiful thief?

726
00:32:56,060 --> 00:32:57,920
Is that a compliment or an insult?

727
00:32:58,310 --> 00:32:59,040
Give it back.

728
00:32:59,790 --> 00:33:00,790
What's your name?

729
00:33:01,300 --> 00:33:02,500
Why should I tell you?

730
00:33:04,710 --> 00:33:05,750
I've got

731
00:33:06,620 --> 00:33:07,760
my eyes on you.

732
00:33:10,260 --> 00:33:11,260
My name is Dan Zhu.

733
00:33:11,950 --> 00:33:12,870
I'm a painter.

734
00:33:13,430 --> 00:33:15,030
I do murals at Guangde Temple.

735
00:33:15,030 --> 00:33:17,140
You can come see me there anytime.

736
00:33:17,470 --> 00:33:18,910
He said this is called Flying Light.

737
00:33:18,910 --> 00:33:20,590
A small bottle of it is worth 3 golden cakes,

738
00:33:20,590 --> 00:33:22,110
and you have to make a reservation 5 days in advance.

739
00:33:22,110 --> 00:33:22,940
But he wouldn't tell us

740
00:33:22,940 --> 00:33:24,070
what the use of it is.

741
00:33:26,350 --> 00:33:27,310
Dan Zhu?

742
00:33:28,390 --> 00:33:29,990
I've heard of this painter.

743
00:33:30,500 --> 00:33:31,630
She's quite famous.

744
00:33:32,070 --> 00:33:33,940
This was bought from the painting shop.

745
00:33:33,940 --> 00:33:35,740
You must have seen Xijun, right?

746
00:33:37,190 --> 00:33:38,560
I actually haven't.

747
00:33:41,350 --> 00:33:42,620
We can only ask him.

748
00:33:53,960 --> 00:33:56,020
Are you here to take me as your master?

749
00:33:58,120 --> 00:33:59,870
I'm not in the mood anymore.

750
00:33:59,910 --> 00:34:01,470
Please leave here

751
00:34:01,490 --> 00:34:02,770
and leave me alone.

752
00:34:05,910 --> 00:34:06,430
Master.

753
00:34:07,070 --> 00:34:08,020
My sworn brother is here

754
00:34:08,020 --> 00:34:09,420
to pick your brain today.

755
00:34:13,389 --> 00:34:15,190
You're an official.

756
00:34:15,750 --> 00:34:17,830
All you have to do is social climbing.

757
00:34:18,070 --> 00:34:19,230
You know nothing about painting.

758
00:34:19,230 --> 00:34:20,670
What do you have to ask me?

759
00:34:20,830 --> 00:34:21,230
You...

760
00:34:24,469 --> 00:34:25,030
Mr. Qin.

761
00:34:25,790 --> 00:34:27,980
I have something to show you.

762
00:34:33,139 --> 00:34:34,670
Mr. Qin, please take a look.

763
00:34:35,030 --> 00:34:36,530
This thing's called Flying Light,

764
00:34:36,530 --> 00:34:37,090
right?

765
00:34:39,949 --> 00:34:40,909
Why did you

766
00:34:40,940 --> 00:34:42,300
bring this to me?

767
00:34:42,330 --> 00:34:43,380
What an eyesore!

768
00:34:44,469 --> 00:34:45,800
Don't do that.

769
00:34:46,030 --> 00:34:47,350
It wasn't easy to get.

770
00:34:47,389 --> 00:34:48,489
If you don't want to see it,

771
00:34:48,489 --> 00:34:49,780
I... I'll put it away.

772
00:34:50,400 --> 00:34:51,510
But Mr. Qin.

773
00:34:52,460 --> 00:34:54,190
Why do you hate

774
00:34:54,590 --> 00:34:56,050
this Flying Light so much?

775
00:35:03,490 --> 00:35:04,450
Rumor has it that

776
00:35:04,490 --> 00:35:06,220
after the Mara escaped the wall and did evil,

777
00:35:06,220 --> 00:35:08,990
this mysterious paint suddenly appeared.

778
00:35:08,990 --> 00:35:10,870
I suspect there are connections between the two events.

779
00:35:10,870 --> 00:35:13,830
Please tell me everything you know, Mr. Qin.

780
00:35:16,690 --> 00:35:17,950
The Flying Light

781
00:35:19,350 --> 00:35:20,150
is the Mara.

782
00:35:22,910 --> 00:35:24,370
This thing came into being

783
00:35:24,390 --> 00:35:25,430
before late Wei.

784
00:35:25,450 --> 00:35:27,510
It was originally named Flying Light

785
00:35:27,970 --> 00:35:29,830
because it was no ordinary paint.

786
00:35:31,070 --> 00:35:32,140
Its main ingredients are

787
00:35:32,140 --> 00:35:33,700
Azurite and Silverfish.

788
00:35:34,130 --> 00:35:35,670
In addition,

789
00:35:35,670 --> 00:35:37,670
there are many other mixed ingredients in it.

790
00:35:37,670 --> 00:35:39,730
There are different rumors about it.

791
00:35:40,680 --> 00:35:41,750
But this evil being

792
00:35:41,790 --> 00:35:43,270
has long been judged

793
00:35:43,290 --> 00:35:44,250
as a taboo item.

794
00:35:45,030 --> 00:35:46,150
You are a government official.

795
00:35:46,150 --> 00:35:47,410
How could you not know?

796
00:35:47,580 --> 00:35:49,430
I... I really didn’t know that.

797
00:35:52,300 --> 00:35:53,100
It is said that

798
00:35:54,450 --> 00:35:56,580
the painting finished by Flying Light

799
00:35:59,010 --> 00:36:00,860
can be incredibly lifelike.

800
00:36:02,220 --> 00:36:02,750
Now,

801
00:36:03,270 --> 00:36:05,600
various temples are competing in murals.

802
00:36:06,180 --> 00:36:07,060
Many painters

803
00:36:07,090 --> 00:36:08,650
spend a lot of money

804
00:36:08,680 --> 00:36:09,790
on this taboo item

805
00:36:09,790 --> 00:36:11,310
to boost their status.

806
00:36:11,330 --> 00:36:12,050
Shameless.

807
00:36:15,790 --> 00:36:16,790
Do you know

808
00:36:18,870 --> 00:36:19,870
why I, Qin Xiaobai,

809
00:36:19,870 --> 00:36:22,310
still haven't done the finishing touch?

810
00:36:25,540 --> 00:36:27,940
It's because I want to do my finishing touch

811
00:36:28,170 --> 00:36:30,430
better than Flying Light with ordinary paints.

812
00:36:30,430 --> 00:36:31,200
Only in this way

813
00:36:31,200 --> 00:36:32,030
can I live up to

814
00:36:32,030 --> 00:36:34,090
the title of the Best Painter of Tang.

815
00:36:38,400 --> 00:36:40,660
Thank you, Mr. Qin, for enlightening us.

816
00:36:43,700 --> 00:36:45,300
After hearing what you said,

817
00:36:45,310 --> 00:36:46,640
I sincerely admire you.

818
00:36:46,800 --> 00:36:47,420
I believe

819
00:36:47,640 --> 00:36:49,860
you can successfully add the finishing touch

820
00:36:49,860 --> 00:36:51,540
and complete this great work.

821
00:36:52,410 --> 00:36:53,140
At that time,

822
00:36:53,550 --> 00:36:54,550
if you don't mind,

823
00:36:55,270 --> 00:36:56,110
I, Pei Xijun,

824
00:36:56,550 --> 00:36:57,150
would like

825
00:36:57,560 --> 00:36:58,870
to be your apprentice.

826
00:37:01,670 --> 00:37:02,590
Should we confiscate

827
00:37:02,590 --> 00:37:04,070
Shenzhu Painting Shop right away?

828
00:37:04,070 --> 00:37:05,420
Don't alert them.

829
00:37:05,670 --> 00:37:07,510
We should start by investigating the raw materials.

830
00:37:07,510 --> 00:37:08,550
Although Azurite is rare,

831
00:37:08,010 --> 00:37:14,340
[Great Buddha Hall]

832
00:37:09,470 --> 00:37:10,470
Chang'an is such a big city.

833
00:37:10,470 --> 00:37:12,330
I believe we can buy it somewhere.

834
00:37:12,560 --> 00:37:13,960
What is this Silverfish?

835
00:37:14,590 --> 00:37:16,670
A Silverfish is a bookworm.

836
00:37:17,170 --> 00:37:17,890
It's the silver white shiny thing

837
00:37:17,890 --> 00:37:19,730
in the powder.

838
00:37:21,120 --> 00:37:22,190
I, Su Wuming,

839
00:37:22,220 --> 00:37:25,550
have been studying for most of my life, but I didn't think of that.

840
00:37:25,550 --> 00:37:26,550
Bookworms?

841
00:37:27,310 --> 00:37:28,640
They're so hard to find.

842
00:37:28,750 --> 00:37:31,630
It takes a lot of bookworms to make Flying Light.

843
00:37:32,750 --> 00:37:34,030
Where can we get them?

844
00:37:36,230 --> 00:37:37,060
Bookstores.

845
00:37:38,440 --> 00:37:39,830
There are only limited number of books

846
00:37:39,830 --> 00:37:41,160
in bookstores.

847
00:37:41,190 --> 00:37:43,550
Besides, most of them are new books.

848
00:37:44,190 --> 00:37:44,730
Brother.

849
00:37:45,370 --> 00:37:46,500
The Palace Library.

850
00:37:47,180 --> 00:37:47,930
Right.

851
00:37:48,680 --> 00:37:50,700
There are more than tens of thousands of books there.

852
00:37:50,700 --> 00:37:52,960
Besides, they're mainly ancient books.

853
00:37:53,070 --> 00:37:56,750
They must have the most bookworms.

854
00:37:58,040 --> 00:37:59,770
[Palace Library]

855
00:38:01,550 --> 00:38:02,360
Su Wuming.

856
00:38:03,390 --> 00:38:05,390
Do you know the skill of divination?

857
00:38:07,070 --> 00:38:09,640
I'm not that capable, Directorate.

858
00:38:10,500 --> 00:38:11,870
Then how do you know that someone in the Palace Library

859
00:38:11,870 --> 00:38:14,070
has been secretly catching bookworms?

860
00:38:28,310 --> 00:38:28,910
Liang Zhi.

861
00:38:29,490 --> 00:38:30,550
What are you doing?

862
00:38:30,990 --> 00:38:34,130
[Liang Zhi from Palace Library]

863
00:38:32,010 --> 00:38:34,420
I was looking for the works of Wei

864
00:38:35,030 --> 00:38:35,960
when I found that

865
00:38:36,110 --> 00:38:37,480
the books are too old.

866
00:38:37,990 --> 00:38:39,270
They're full of bookworms.

867
00:38:39,270 --> 00:38:41,770
I was worried that the books might be damaged,

868
00:38:41,770 --> 00:38:43,030
so I came to catch them.

869
00:38:43,030 --> 00:38:44,960
All the books here are ancient books,

870
00:38:44,960 --> 00:38:46,450
